  "title": "Pega Build Lead / Senior Developer (Ref 25481)",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities<br />• As a Lead/Senior Application Developer, you will be responsible for designing, building, and configuring applications to meet business process and application requirements. <br />• You are expected to be a subject matter expert, collaborate and manage the team to perform effectively. <br />• You will be responsible for team decisions, engage with multiple teams, and contribute to key decisions. <br />• Additionally, you will provide solutions to problems for your immediate team and across multiple teams. <br />• Advanced proficiency in Pega Platform is required. <br />• Advanced proficiency in Design & Build Enablement is recommended. <br />• Advanced proficiency in Configuration & Release Management is suggested.<br />• Develop innovative application solutions that enhance user experience and meet client needs.<br />• Conduct thorough testing and validation of applications to ensure functionality and performance.<br />• Collaborate with cross-functional teams to gather requirements and provide technical insights.<br />• Mentor junior team members and share best practices to foster a culture of continuous improvement.<br /><br />Requirements<br />• Degree / Diploma in Computer Studies or equivalent<br />• Minimum of 2 years of hands-on experience in Pega development and Pega CSA certified</p><p>Licence no: 12C6060</p>",
